English.ChangelogsText:
<font color="rgb(76, 0, 255)">Release v2.7</font>

<font color="rgb(255, 255, 255)">-- ESP & Visuals --</font>
- <font color="rgb(0, 255, 0)">Added Glitch Cube to Item ESP table</font>
